OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's life and alter-ego to
OL,4,Cbe celebrated in new stage comedy
OL,6,FA brand-new comedy and drag show
OL,7,Fcelebrating the life of Paul O'Grady
OL,8,Fand his legendary alter ego Lily
OL,9,FSavage will make its world premiere in
OL,10,F2027.
OL,12,FThe production, titled SAVAGE, has
OL,13,Fbeen written by multi-award-winning
OL,14,Fscreenwriter and playwright Jonathan
OL,15,FHarvey, who is best known for Gimme
OL,16,FGimme Gimme, Coronation Street and
OL,17,FBeautiful Thing.
OL,19,FIt will star RuPaul's Drag Race UK
OL,20,Fwinner Danny Beard, from Liverpool, in
OL,21,Fthe title role.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
