OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's life and alter-ego to
OL,4,Cbe celebrated in new stage comedy
OL,6,FCreated with Paul O'Grady's blessing
OL,7,Fbefore his passing in March 2023, the
OL,8,Fnew play draws on both his
OL,9,Fextraordinary life and his
OL,10,Fautobiographies to tell the true story
OL,11,Fbehind the creation of Lily Savage.
OL,13,FIt follows Paul's journey from the
OL,14,Fstreets of Merseyside to the heart of
OL,15,FLondon's club scene, where he began
OL,16,Fcarving out a place for himself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
