OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's life and alter-ego to
OL,4,Cbe celebrated in new stage comedy
OL,6,FProducers promise an intimate portrait
OL,7,Fthat is "funny, raw, and full of
OL,8,Fheart," combining razor-sharp wit,
OL,9,Funexpected tenderness, and "plenty of
OL,10,Fperoxide" to tell the story of how
OL,11,FPaul became Lily, and how Lily became
OL,12,Fa British icon.
OL,14,FWriter Jonathan Harvey said: "It's an
OL,15,Fhonour indeed to bring his story and
OL,16,Fthe colourful escapades of the blonde
OL,17,Fbombsite herself to life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
