PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781615476
OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's life and alter-ego to
OL,4,Cbe celebrated in new stage comedy
OL,6,F"This is one of those few shows that
OL,7,FI'm involved in where I can go 'You
OL,8,Fneed to come. It's really
OL,9,Fgood'...because the zinging one-liners
OL,10,Fare all his.
OL,12,F"It's so sad he's not here to see it,
OL,13,Fbut hopefully this will be a fitting
OL,14,Ftestament to everything he achieved,
OL,15,Fand a cracking night out full of
OL,16,Fhumour and heart."
OL,18,FThe production will be directed by
OL,19,FCurve Artistic Director Nikolai
OL,20,FFoster, known for Kinky Boots and
OL,21,FLegally Blonde.
OL,26,@xD@RO]
