OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781615476
OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's life and alter-ego to
OL,4,Cbe celebrated in new stage comedy
OL,6,FIt will premiere at Curve Leicester on
OL,7,F13 February 2027, then head to
OL,8,FLiverpool Playhouse, the Lowry in
OL,9,FSalford, Canterbury's Marlowe Theatre,
OL,10,FTheatre Royal Bath, Norwich Theatre
OL,11,FRoyal, and Birmingham Hippodrome.
OL,13,FThe show will then have a stint on
OL,14,FLondon's West End. Tickets go on
OL,15,Fgeneral sale 16 June at 10am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
